                        p In this website you can take a look at existing pizzas or propose your idea
            .row
                .col-sm-4
                    img.img-responsive(src='images/ham_potato.png', style='width:100%', alt='Image')
                    p Ham and Potatos
                .col-sm-4
                    img.img-responsive(src='images/pizza-wurstel-patatine.jpg', style='width:100%', alt='Image')
                    p Potatos and Wurstel
                .col-sm-4
                    img.img-responsive(src='images/bresaola_rucola.jpg', style='width:100%', alt='Image')
                    p Bresaola and Rucola
                    //.well
                        p Contribute with your Fantasy!
